snippet.title: Major Stryker gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Major Stryker, Dos PC game produced by Apogee in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/major-stryker/5956/
Playing this vertical scrollin flight shooter arcade. Running a couple of levels.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
